Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! LDR Brands is the collaboration between two recovering sports and entertainment executives who grew tired of the lack of available luxury accessory options tailor-made to meet the distinct needs of the female traveler. Built originally to suffice their own accessories needs as women on-the-go, LDR Brands is now an all encompassing luxury accessories brand with a wide range of innovative product offerings and styles. Long time friends and founders, Nickole and Sarah often joked that they were in a long distance relationship with one another while maintaining their bicoastal lifestyles in NYC and LA. And hence, LDR Brands was a fitting name for the company built over years of long distance communication and airport meet-ups. LDR Brands' debut product, The Porter, offered the first savvy merging of functionality and style in a 100% leather configuration with it's unique half moon silhouette. You can find more of their products on ldrbrands.com and in fine boutique retail across the country. - Pebbled leather and suede with shock absorbent padding in computer section - Pen and lipgloss holder, key/cord keeper - Interior business card and phone pocket with secure zipper and exterior zipper pocket and phone pocket slot - Fit for a 13" laptop and has a 7" handle drop with an adjustable strap - 16.5"L x 3"W x 12.75"H, 3lb.
